sources.title: Albert Peckingpaw's Revenge 1968 | Jack Lester - Hicksploitation - By James Landis | 4K
sources.description:
Jennie Peckingpaw schemes a cash harvest from her crusty husband Albert, drafting farmhand Mario into a high-stakes field operation—but when Albert’s suspicion sprouts into a shotgun reckoning, their escape plan becomes a dusty duel of desperation.

Original title: Jennie: Wife/Child (1968)

Directed and Written by James Landis, Co-directed by Robert Carl Cohen

Main cast:
Jack Lester - Albert Peckingpaw
Beverly Lunsford - Jennie Peckingpaw
Jim Reader - Mario Dingle
Virginia Wood - Lulu Belle
Richard Cowl - Dr. Hill
Release date: November 1968


Black & White version: https://youtu.be/FBRo1mXxZ94

Audio commentary version: https://youtu.be/CTzbxcPUeAU
